WEBVTT

00:11.530 --> 00:13.609
Why would you do that?

00:13.610 --> 00:15.954
Do what?

00:15.955 --> 00:17.239
Jump.

00:54.990 --> 00:56.739
If I wanna be happy,

00:56.740 --> 00:58.759
I have to get away from you.

01:00.457 --> 01:01.949
Hey, buddy.

01:01.950 --> 01:03.875
Dude.

01:17.890 --> 01:19.182
I said shut up.

01:19.183 --> 01:21.419
- Where is she, asshole?
- Fuck you...

01:21.420 --> 01:22.430
Where is she?

01:35.650 --> 01:38.869
You're okay, you're okay. Are you okay?

01:50.965 --> 01:53.499
